description:
Photoshop Elements has been saving many people money by not having to buy Photoshop. I have been teaching Photoshop Elements since version 1 and it still amazes me today with what I can do with my editing.

I will walk you through the Organizer where we will begin to get all of our pictures organized and make it easier to find them in this Photoshop Elements Tutorial. We will then begin to learn to edit our pictures using some great easy to use tools.

Also this course always has room to grow as I design new edits I will add them to the course so you can grow with this course over time.

Please join me and begin to get your digital photography organized and allow your creative side to flow by learning How to Use Photoshop Elements.

</p>
title: Photoshop Elements 11/12 Road to Great Pictures
